race.description: Tabtouch Pinjarra Classic Punters Club Feb 22 Maiden
race.comment: YOU CAN CALL ME AL (3) missed narrowly two back before a 0.3L defeat last start over the mile on the main track here. The inside draw suits and the form out of his last start has stacked up well. Whiting hops back on board and he can go one better this time around. THE ROCKET (9) will find this a little easier than his recent effort over the 1400m trip at this track most recently. Maps beautifully again today with the 2kg claim of ZJP. Wouldn't surprise to see him come out on top with the slight rise in trip. BRADBURY'S MOMENT (5) was solid in a 3YO Saturday race last start when closing well over 1400m at Ascot. Fiore hops back on board now as he drops in grade. Should be suited by the rise in trip and can land the knockout blow. COMMON TOUCH (8) missed as favourite over the mile here last start but is better than that. Won't be far away. PRESSURISED (11) is out of G1 Railway Stakes winner Galaxy Star on debut. Can put her best foot forward on debut.
